---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const siteName = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_NAME ?? "PricingNest";
---
<BaseLayout
  title={`Annual Prepay Discount | ${siteName}`}
  description="Annual prepay discount definition, how to choose a discount, and how to sanity-check it with break-even thinking."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Annual prepay discount</h1>
    <p>An annual prepay discount trades a lower effective monthly price for commitment and upfront cash.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="grid">
    <article class="card col8">
      <h2>What the discount is buying</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li><strong>Lower churn</strong>: annual commitment can reduce cancellations.</li>
        <li><strong>Lower collection overhead</strong>: fewer billing events.</li>
        <li><strong>Cash now</strong>: improves runway even if total value is unchanged.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">How to choose a discount</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Start small (5â€“15%) unless you have a strong retention reason.</li>
        <li>Prefer discounting commitment, not just time (e.g., annual + higher minimums).</li>
        <li>Compare discount cost to churn reduction and sales efficiency.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">Tools to use</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li><a href="/saas-pricing/annual-discount-calculator/">Annual discount calculator</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guides/annual-prepay-discount/">Guide: break-even discount</a></li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <aside class="card col4">
      <h2>Related</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li><a href="/glossary/churn/">Churn</a></li>
        <li><a href="/glossary/mrr/">MRR</a></li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

